        =======
        History
        =======
        
        0.1.0 (2018-04-21)
        ------------------
        
        * First release on PyPI.
        
        0.1.2 (2019-04-04)
        ------------------
        
        * Add elasticity operators.
        
        
        0.2.0 (2019-12-02)
        ------------------
        
        * Python 2 support dropped.
        
        * Fix vector gradient for curvilinear coordinates.
        
        * Add divergence for second-order tensors.
        
